      <h1>Forskrift om endring i forskrift til oppl&#xE6;ringslova</h1>
      <section class="section" data-name="kapI" id="kapittel-1" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/2020-09-16-1778/KAPITTEL_1">
        <h2 data-text-align="center">I</h2>
        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1">I forskrift 23. juni 2006 nr. 724 til oppl&#xE6;ringslova skal &#xA7; 24-2 andre ledd lyde:</article>
        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2">Siste eksamen i fag etter LK06/LK06S skal haldast hausten etter f&#xF8;rste eksamen for LK20/LK20S. Siste eksamen etter LK06/LK06S for dei ulike trinna i vidareg&#xE5;ande skal haldast:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-1"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-1-ledd-1">hausten 2021 for vidareg&#xE5;ande trinn 1</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-2"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-2-ledd-1">hausten 2022 for vidareg&#xE5;ande trinn 2</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-3"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-2-punkt-3-ledd-1">hausten 2023 for vidareg&#xE5;ande trinn 3.</article></article></li></ul></article>
      </section>
